- Dec 28, 2015 (lsiden@gmail.com)

* Updated README with instructions for testing.
* Added "license" field to bower.json and package.json
* Added "description" field to bower.json and package.json.
* Added "repository" field to bower.json and package.json.
* Prompt for description and gitUrl.
* Create example.html file to demo new component.
* Support template caching for templateUrl in directive $compile options.
* Added package.json dependencies to support template caching:
  - event-stream
  - gulp-angular-templatecache
  - karma-ng-html2js-preprocessor
  - ng-html2js
* Support concatenation of stylesheets (.css and .scss) for directive modules.
* Added package.json dependencies to support stylesheet pipeline:
  - gulp-scss
